#: ../../../../release/_9.6-stripped.md:52
msgid ""
"**Scalar Bar Vertical Title Separation** The `VerticalTitleSeparation` "
"property in a scalar bar controls the distance between the title of the "
"scalar bar and the color bar itself when the title is oriented vertically. "
"This property is now applied even for horizontal scalar bars, ensuring "
"consistent spacing regardless of orientation."
