#: ../../../../release/_9.6-stripped.md:276
msgid ""
"**Faster vtkDataAssembly node traversal** Unify implementation of "
"`IsNodeNameReserved` and add short-circuiting logic to optimize for typical "
"usage. Improves performance of `GetChild` and dependent methods by about 50%."
msgstr ""

#: ../../../../release/_9.6-stripped.md:278
msgid ""
"**Performance: Faster observer operations in vtkObject** `vtkObject` now "
"stores observers in a `std::map`. `AddObserver` and `RemoveObserver` both "
"use a binary search, providing O(log n) runtime per operation. ([Author "
"notes](9.6/optimize-vtkObserver.md))"
msgstr ""

