msgstr ""

#: ../../../../release/_9.6-stripped.md:283
msgid ""
"**vtkAbstractArray: Replace most instances of GetVoidPointer** Approximately "
"75% of `GetVoidPointer()` usages have been removed to reduce unnecessary "
"data duplication and copying overhead. ([Author notes](9.6/replace-"
"GetVoidPointer-usages.md))"
msgstr ""

#: ../../../../release/_9.6-stripped.md:285
msgid ""
"**vtkArrayDispatch: Dispatch known Arrays with O(1) complexity** The "
"`vtkArrayDispatch` mechanism has been optimized to O(1) complexity, "
"regardless of the number of given arrays, by adding compile-time known tags "
"to each VTK array."
msgstr ""

#: ../../../../release/_9.6-stripped.md:287
msgid ""
"**vtkDataArrayPrivate: Improve DoCompute(Scalar/Vector)Range Performance** "
"`DoComputeScalarRange` and `DoComputeVectorRange` have been optimized to "
"enhance performance by about 2x."
msgstr ""

#: ../../../../release/_9.6-stripped.md:289
msgid ""
"**vtkFieldData performance** Copying `vtkFieldData` structures with "
"`DeepCopy` and `PassData` is now faster (up to 70x/180x speedup observed) by "
"assuming uniqueness in the source."
msgstr ""

#: ../../../../release/_9.6-stripped.md:291
msgid ""
"**vtkMaybeUnused macro removal** The `vtkMaybeUnused` macro was not "
"functional and has been removed. Use the `[[maybe_unused]]` attribute "
"instead."
msgstr ""

#: ../../../../release/_9.6-stripped.md:296
msgid ""
"**Cell status enumeration, vtkPolygon, and vtkPolyhedron** The enumeration "
"of defects detected by `vtkCellValidator` has been expanded and moved to "
"`vtkCellStatus.h`. `vtkPolygon` and `vtkPolyhedron` now report additional "
"defects."
msgstr ""

#: ../../../../release/_9.6-stripped.md:299
msgid "![new-cell-validator-status-bits](imgs/9.6/cell-status.png)"
msgstr ""

#: ../../../../release/_9.6-stripped.md:299
msgid "new-cell-validator-status-bits"
msgstr ""

#: ../../../../release/_9.6-stripped.md:301
msgid ""
"**Fix vtkQuadricDecimation point data attributes** Fixed regression where "
"PointData attributes were incorrectly computed."
msgstr ""

#: ../../../../release/_9.6-stripped.md:303
msgid ""
"**Improve vtkBlockIdScalars** `vtkBlockIdScalars` now supports any "
"`vtkDataObjectTree`, which includes `vtkPartitionedDataSetCollection`. It "
"also supports iterating into a composite hierarchy."
msgstr ""

#: ../../../../release/_9.6-stripped.md:305
msgid ""
"**vtkArrayCalculator: Enable vector definition of arbitrary size** "
"`vtkArrayCalculator` now supports user-defined vectors of arbitrary size "
"using the `{x, y, z, ...}` syntax."
msgstr ""

#: ../../../../release/_9.6-stripped.md:307
msgid ""
"**vtkDataSet: GetCellTypes updates** `vtkDataSet::GetCellTypes` has been "
"deprecated in favor of `GetDistinctCellTypes`. `vtkUnstructuredGrid` now "
"uses `vtkDataArray` for cell types to allow for `vtkConstantArray<unsigned "
"char>`."
msgstr ""

#: ../../../../release/_9.6-stripped.md:309
msgid ""
"**vtkmDataArray: Fix thread-safety issues** Fixed thread-safety issues in "
"`GetTuple`/`SetTuple` by adding a mutex to protect the internal array handle "
"swap."
msgstr ""

#: ../../../../release/_9.6-stripped.md:311
msgid ""
"**Fixed Template Array Serialization** VTK now correctly serializes template "
"arrays. This fix ensures that template array types are properly handled "
"during serialization, improving compatibility between Python and WebAssembly "
"(WASM) builds."
msgstr ""

#: ../../../../release/_9.6-stripped.md:316
msgid ""
"**Correct thresholding behavior in vtkThresholdPoints** `vtkThresholdPoints` "
"now uses the same rules as `vtkThreshold` for both lower and upper bounds."
msgstr ""

#: ../../../../release/_9.6-stripped.md:318
msgid ""
"**Fix cubic interpolation for small image dimensions** The cubic "
"interpolation mode of `vtkImageInterpolator` no longer gives incorrect "
"results for input images with small dimensions."
msgstr ""

#: ../../../../release/_9.6-stripped.md:320
msgid ""
"**Fix distributed HTG ghost cells issues** Ghost array is now correctly "
"added to distributed HTG when ghost cells are requested, and HTG metadata is "
"properly exchanged."
msgstr ""

#: ../../../../release/_9.6-stripped.md:322
msgid ""
"**Fix interpolate scalars before mapping in surface LIC mappers** A scalar "
"mapping bug has been fixed in the surface LIC mappers. Interpolation now "
"correctly occurs before mapping the scalars to colors when the flag is "
"enabled."
msgstr ""

#: ../../../../release/_9.6-stripped.md:324
msgid ""
"**Fix retrieval of the closest point in vtkStaticPointLocator** The function "
"`IntersectWithLine` of `vtkStaticPointLocator` now always retrieves the "
"closest point."
msgstr ""

#: ../../../../release/_9.6-stripped.md:326
msgid ""
"**Fix vtkCleanPolyData large tolerance** `vtkCleanPolyData` now supports "
"large tolerance. Mesh stays watertight in case of large tolerance."
msgstr ""

#: ../../../../release/_9.6-stripped.md:328
msgid ""
"**Improve the clipping performance for polyhedrons** Clipping operations on "
"unstructured grids composed mostly of polyhedron cells are now significantly "
"faster (up to 300x)."
msgstr ""

#: ../../../../release/_9.6-stripped.md:330
msgid ""
"**Large tolerance in vtkCleanPolyData** `vtkCleanPolyData` now supports "
"large tolerance. Mesh stays watertight and cells no longer disappear "
"arbitrarily."
msgstr ""

#: ../../../../release/_9.6-stripped.md:332
msgid ""
"**vtkAxisAlignedReflectionFilter: Improve Assembly Construction for PDC** "
"`vtkAxisAlignedReflectionFilter` now constructs the output `vtkDataAssembly` "
"by reflecting the input assembly, preserving the hierarchical structure."
msgstr ""

#: ../../../../release/_9.6-stripped.md:334
msgid ""
"**vtkColorTransferFunction: Consider Hue as circular for diverging "
"interpolation** `vtkColorTransferFunction` has been updated to consider that "
"Hue may be circular when performing diverging interpolation."
msgstr ""

#: ../../../release_details/9.6.md:5
msgid ""
"![Diverging Interpolation Before](imgs/9.6/diverging-interpolation-before."
"png)"
msgstr ""

#: ../../../../release/_9.6-stripped.md:339
msgid "Diverging Interpolation Before"
msgstr ""

#: ../../../release_details/9.6.md:5
msgid ""
"![Diverging Interpolation After](imgs/9.6/diverging-interpolation-after.png)"
msgstr ""

#: ../../../../release/_9.6-stripped.md:339
msgid "Diverging Interpolation After"
msgstr ""

#: ../../../../release/_9.6-stripped.md:342
msgid ""
"**vtkMeshQuality: Add non-linear cells support** The `vtkMeshQuality` filter "
"has been updated to expose `Verdict` metrics for non-linear cells (e.g., "
"`vtkQuadraticTriangle`, `vtkQuadraticHexahedron`)."
msgstr ""

#: ../../../../release/_9.6-stripped.md:344
msgid ""
"**vtkRedistributeDataSetFilter: fix missing cells in ASSIGN_TO_ONE_REGION "
"mode** Concave cells that lie on the boundary of multiple partitions could "
"be deleted in this mode; this is now fixed."
msgstr ""

#: ../../../../release/_9.6-stripped.md:346
msgid ""
"**vtkSurfaceNets3D: Fix Consistent Normal Orientation** `vtkSurfaceNets3D` "
"now generates meshes with consistent normal orientations."
msgstr ""

#: ../../../../release/_9.6-stripped.md:348
msgid ""
"**vtkTableBasedClipDataSet: Add GenerateClipPointType** "
"`vtkTableBasedClipDataSet` now includes a new option called "
"`GenerateClipPointType` that allows users to specify whether to generate a "
"point array specifying the type of each point (input, edge, or centroid)."
msgstr ""

#: ../../../../release/_9.6-stripped.md:350
msgid ""
"**vtkTableBasedClipDataSet: Fix Clipping Duplicating Points** "
"`vtkTableBasedClipDataSet` no longer duplicates points when processing cells "
"that are not supported by it."
msgstr ""

#: ../../../../release/_9.6-stripped.md:355
msgid ""
"**Fix wrong default value of vtkXMLUniformGridAMRReader::"
"MaximumLevelsToReadByDefault** Default value is now 0 (infinite) as "
"documented, instead of 1."
msgstr ""

#: ../../../../release/_9.6-stripped.md:357
msgid ""
"**HyperTreeGridXMLReader: support Coordinates Bounding box for V2 files** "
"Add support for `CoordinatesBoundingBox` in `vtkXMLHyperTreeGridReader` for "
"files with major version 2."
msgstr ""

#: ../../../../release/_9.6-stripped.md:359
msgid ""
"**Improve glTF camera focal point** Introduced a `vtkGLTFImporter::"
"GuessCamerasFocalPoints()` called at the end of the import to assign a less "
"arbitrary focal point based on the imported actors."
msgstr ""

#: ../../../../release/_9.6-stripped.md:361
msgid ""
"**Improve Importers animation API** `vtkImporter::GetTemporalInformation` "
"has been reworked and now provides a simpler API."
msgstr ""

#: ../../../../release/_9.6-stripped.md:363
msgid ""
"**Only keep first array if duplicated names in XML readers** When reading a "
"dataset with multiple arrays with the same name, a warning is displayed and "
"only the first one is kept."
msgstr ""

#: ../../../../release/_9.6-stripped.md:365
msgid ""
"**Support multimesh protocol in vtkDataObjectToConduit** Add serialization "
"support for composite structures in `vtkDataObjectToConduit`, using the "
"multimesh protocol."
msgstr ""

#: ../../../../release/_9.6-stripped.md:367
msgid ""
"**vtkDataObjectToConduit improvements** `vtkDataObjectToConduit` improves "
"support for mixed-shape polydata meshes, polygons, triangle strips, poly "
"lines, and poly vertex cells."
msgstr ""

#: ../../../../release/_9.6-stripped.md:369
msgid ""
"**vtkIOSSReader: Change Catalyst Conduit channel name** `vtkIOSSReader` now "
"supports changing the Catalyst Conduit channel name when reading from IOSS "
"catalyst databases."
msgstr ""

#: ../../../../release/_9.6-stripped.md:371
msgid ""
"**vtkIOSSReader: Distributed read of a single file using netCDF parallel** "
"The `vtkIOSSReader` now supports reading a single IOSS file in parallel "
"using the netCDF parallel I/O capabilities."
msgstr ""

#: ../../../../release/_9.6-stripped.md:373
msgid ""
"**vtkIOSSWriter: Write tensor arrays as tensors** `vtkIOSSWriter` now writes "
"tensor arrays as tensors instead of separate scalar components."
msgstr ""

#: ../../../../release/_9.6-stripped.md:375
msgid ""
"**vtkMultiProcessStream: Support for vtkDataArray and vtkStringArray** "
"`vtkMultiProcessStream` has been updated to support `vtkDataArray` and "
"`vtkStringArray`."
msgstr ""

#: ../../../../release/_9.6-stripped.md:380
msgid ""
"**Fix Bi-dimensional widget 2D representation for any view plane** The "
"`vtkBiDimensionalRepresentation2D` has been generalized to handle view "
"planes other than the XY plane in world coordinates."
msgstr ""

#: ../../../../release/_9.6-stripped.md:382
msgid ""
"**Fix Cocoa timer crash** Fixed a macOS crash when timers restart after "
"interactor destruction (`vtkCocoaRenderWindowInteractor`)."
msgstr ""

#: ../../../../release/_9.6-stripped.md:384
msgid ""
"**Fix update of properties in vtkLineRepresentation and add setters** The "
"`vtkProperty` of elements of `vtkLineRepresentation` is now correctly "
"updated."
msgstr ""

#: ../../../../release/_9.6-stripped.md:386
msgid ""
"**Improve box widget/representation** The box widget can now be rotated "
"along a single axis by holding the x, y, or z key. Scaling interaction has "
"also been improved."
msgstr ""

#: ../../../../release/_9.6-stripped.md:391
msgid ""
"**Python object property setter argument types** The setter method called "
"when setting an object property in Python is now the same regardless of "
"whether a tuple or a list is used. If a multi-argument setter exists, it is "
"used."
msgstr ""

#: ../../../../release/_9.6-stripped.md:393
msgid ""
"**VTK SDK as wheels are now available on the wheel-sdks repository** The VTK "
"wheel SDK is now packaged directly as Python wheels (.whl)."
msgstr ""

#: ../../../../release/_9.6-stripped.md:396
msgid "Java"
msgstr ""

#: ../../../../release/_9.6-stripped.md:398
msgid "Fixed several build errors in VTK module-generated Java wrappings."
msgstr ""

#: ../../../../release/_9.6-stripped.md:399
msgid ""
"Restored Java Maven package generation and upload mechanism to Kitware's "
"Maven repository located at https://github.com/orgs/Kitware/packages."
msgstr ""

#: ../../../../release/_9.6-stripped.md:401
msgid "Added Java test jobs that run in VTK's CI."
msgstr ""

#: ../../../../release/_9.6-stripped.md:405
msgid ""
"**ANARI Renderer Introspection** The `vtkAnariRenderer` class now allows "
"users to introspect and query the parameters supported by the chosen ANARI "
"rendering backend."
msgstr ""

#: ../../../../release/_9.6-stripped.md:407
msgid ""
"**Dynamic X11 Function Loading in VTK** VTK now supports dynamic loading of "
"X11 functions through the new `VTK::x11` module. You no longer need a hard "
"X11 dependency."
msgstr ""

#: ../../../../release/_9.6-stripped.md:409
msgid ""
"**Fix reslice gap** Fixed a tolerance issue in `vtkImageReslice` that could "
"cause black slices in rare streaming situations."
msgstr ""

#: ../../../../release/_9.6-stripped.md:411
msgid ""
"**Improve JOGL Integration (JogAmp v2.6.0)** Improved integration with JOGL/"
"JogAmp v2.6.0. Fixed `vtkGenericOpenGLRenderWindow::OpenGLInit()` and "
"ensured seamless OpenGL usage between JOGL and VTK."
msgstr ""

#: ../../../../release/_9.6-stripped.md:413
msgid ""
"**Improved vtkDataSetMapper performance** The newer `vtkGeometryFilter` "
"includes many speedups and is now being used in `vtkDataSetMapper` instead "
"of the older `vtkDataSetSurfaceFilter`."
msgstr ""

#: ../../../../release/_9.6-stripped.md:415
msgid ""
"**Support point size in vtkGlyph3DMapper OpenGL backend in WASM** Fixed a "
"bug where glyphs rendered with point representation appeared very small on "
"WASM/GLES3."
msgstr ""

#: ../../../../release/_9.6-stripped.md:417
msgid ""
"**Fix incorrect connectivity crash** VTK no longer crashes when it renders a "
"`vtkPolyData` with invalid index in the connectivity array of the cells."
msgstr ""

#: ../../../../release/_9.6-stripped.md:422
msgid ""
"**Fix wrapping tools suffix for WASM** The wrapping tools now use a `."
"commonjs` suffix, preventing runtime errors when running with Node.js "
"projects that use `\"type\": \"module\"`."
msgstr ""

#: ../../../../release/_9.6-stripped.md:425
msgid "Deprecations/Removals"
msgstr ""

#: ../../../../release/_9.6-stripped.md:427
msgid ""
"**Deprecated Members Removal**: Removed `vtkHyperTreeGridThreshold::"
"JustCreateNewMask` and `vtkTemporalAlgorithm::RunBackward`."
msgstr ""

#: ../../../../release/_9.6-stripped.md:428
msgid ""
"**Deprecated vtkCollection API with bad spelling**: Deprecated "
"`IndexOfFirstOccurence` in favor of `IndexOfFirstOccurrence`."
msgstr ""

#: ../../../../release/_9.6-stripped.md:429
msgid ""
"**Deprecate unused vtkHyperTree(Grid) methods and options**: `vtkHyperTree::"
"Freeze`, `vtkHyperTreeGrid::Squeeze`, and related members."
msgstr ""

#: ../../../../release/_9.6-stripped.md:430
msgid ""
"**Deprecate vtkUniformGrid methods**: `vtkUniformGrid` is now an empty shell."
msgstr ""

#: ../../../../release/_9.6-stripped.md:431
msgid ""
"**Deprecate vtkmDataSet**: Deprecated since all `vtkmDataArray` can now be "
"stored inside a subclass of `vtkDataSet` as a `vtkDataArray`."
msgstr ""

#: ../../../../release/_9.6-stripped.md:432
msgid ""
"**HyperTreeGridScales Getters deprecation**: Deprecated `GetScales[X/Y/Z]`, "
"replaced by `ComputeScale[X/Y/Z]`."
msgstr ""

#: ../../../../release/_9.6-stripped.md:433
msgid ""
"**vtk::DataArrayValueRange**: Deprecated `data()` method in favor of "
"`begin()`/`end()`."
msgstr ""

#: ../../../../release/_9.6-stripped.md:435
msgid "Updates"
msgstr ""

#: ../../../../release/_9.6-stripped.md:437
msgid ""
"**h5Part: Migrate to h5hut to 2.0.0**: `VTK::h5part` has been replaced by "
"`VTK::h5hut`."
msgstr ""

#: ../../../../release/_9.6-stripped.md:438
msgid "**hdf5**: Updated to 1.14.6."
msgstr ""

#: ../../../../release/_9.6-stripped.md:439
msgid "**Ioss**: Updated to seacas v2025-08-28."
msgstr ""

#: ../../../../release/_9.6-stripped.md:440
msgid "**netCDF**: Updated to 4.9.3."
msgstr ""

#: ../../../../release/_9.6-stripped.md:441
msgid "**Remove double-conversion**: Removed in favor of using `fmt`."
msgstr ""

#: ../../../../release/_9.6-stripped.md:442
msgid "**verdict**: Updated to 1.4.4."
msgstr ""

#: ../../../../release/_9.6-stripped.md:443
msgid "**Viskores**: Updated to 1.1.0."
msgstr ""

#: ../../../../release/_9.6-stripped.md:444
msgid "**fmt**: Updated to 12.1.0."
msgstr ""
